headline: Palo Alto vs. CrowdStrike: Which Cybersecurity Stock Will Outperform in 2025?
summary: 2024 had a lot of ups and downs for two of the world's top cybersecurity companies, CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) and Palo Alto Networks (NASDAQ: PANW).  The former was involved in a highly publicized outage, while the latter made a radical change to its business strategy.  Both stocks ended 2024 with solid returns, with CrowdStrike the better performer.
